Package: concstats
Title: Market Structure and Concentration Measures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Andreas",
           family = "Schneider",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "schneiderconsultingpy@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5630-1097"))
Description: Based on individual market shares of all participants in a market or space, the function calculates a set of
    different structural and concentration measures frequently - and not so frequently - used in research and in practice.
    The resulting vector in table format should help practitioners make more informed decisions.
